    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breeding Grounds is an old school style dungeon crawler. The goal is to progress through various rooms and eventually defeat the final boss, the source of all monsters. You must be quick however, as the miasma leaking from monsters will cause constant damage to your health. You will be able to play as a few different classes, each with their own set of bonuses and drawbacks. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 heroes to choose from, each with different stats and special attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handful of pickups to help you on your journey</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dozen unique enemies and a final boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique regions offering more hazards for you to deal with</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runs that consist of 9 out of 24 randomly selected rooms, plus a tutorial and boss room</p></li></ul>",
